<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٥٨٣٩ - حَدَّثَنِي <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/5638">مُحَمَّدٌ: </a>أَخْبَرَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/6792">وَكِيعٌ: </a>أَخْبَرَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2779">شُعْبَةُ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/5183">قَتَادَةَ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/822">أَنَسٍ </a>قَالَ: <span class="c2">«رَخَّصَ النَّبِيُّ <span class="special">ﷺ</span> لِلزُّبَيْرِ وَعَبْدِ الرَّحْمَنِ فِي لُبْسِ الْحَرِيرِ لِحِكَّةٍ بِهِمَا.»</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>